Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体繁体\fad(0,500)\fs50\fsp8\be25\bord3\shad3\pos(640,555)\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(\fs35)}制 作 人\N伊恩·史密斯
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.10,0:08:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,總統閣下？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体繁体\fad(0,500)\fs50\fsp8\be25\bord3\shad3\pos(640,555)\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(\fs35)}监 制\N布莱恩·格雷泽
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.44,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是西奧多·羅斯福
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.61,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体繁体\fad(0,500)\fs50\fsp8\be25\bord3\shad3\pos(640,555)\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(\fs35)}监 制\N基弗·萨瑟兰
